research_municipality_step.notes: Fate, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government. The Mayor and six Council members are elected for three-year terms on a nonpartisan basis by the entire city. There is an upcoming general election on May 3, 2025, for the Mayor and Council Places 4 and 6. Additionally, a recall petition has been filed against Councilwoman Codi Chinn, with a recall election expected to be on the May ballot.
